How come you're here?

117
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,020
Well, I think...

118
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,261
Jiang Haitao?

119
00:06:38,741 --> 00:06:40,421
Are you Jiang Haitao?

120
00:06:40,981 --> 00:06:41,821
