165
00:08:04,621 --> 00:08:05,621
Come, sit in the back.

166
00:08:05,621 --> 00:08:06,301
Come on.

167
00:08:09,981 --> 00:08:11,100
Auntie, get in the car.

168
00:08:11,981 --> 00:08:13,340
You!

169
